用的是 <strong>有道云</strong> 和 <strong>Notion</strong> 这些产品。</p>\n<p>但是一来 <strong>空间有限</strong> ，二来有时候访问 <strong>速度</strong> 比较尴尬，三来也怕到时跟 <strong>某网盘</strong> 一样，放进去容易取出来难。</p>\n<p>所以想整个 <strong>知识库系统</strong> ，这个项目倒是容易找个来抄抄改改，就是服务器比较麻烦，目前自己用的是 1 核 2 GiB 的 <strong>阿里乞丐版</strong> 。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"阿里乞丐版 1\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0329/082028_dcfcc1aa_7404663.png\"/></p>\n<p>有个问题就是这挂壁服务器老是内存 99.99%，而且一直给我推有安全风险。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"阿里乞丐版 2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0329/082458_b339ba89_7404663.png\"/></p>\n<p>想问下 V2 的大佬们，用啥服务器比较稳定靠谱便宜实惠？或者这种情况要怎么处理啊？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1616977546, "replies": 60, "id": 766000}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/17e6/2166/43_large.png?m=1616741673", "name": "jobs", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/17e6/2166/43_normal.png?m=1616741673", "title": "酷工作", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/jobs", "topics": 47347, "footer": "", "header": "做有趣的有意义的事情。", "title_alternative": "Jobs", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/17e6/2166/43_mini.png?m=1616741673", "stars": 4636, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 43, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"username": "Fatcoder", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0596/089e/51615_mini.png?m=1615358413", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Fatcoder", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1386733688, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0596/089e/51615_mini.png?m=1615358413", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0596/089e/51615_mini.png?m=1615358413", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 51615}, "last_reply_by": "Fatcoder", "last_touched": 1616854675, "title": "[国外远程] 招 react 职位", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/766089", "created": 1616987975, "content": "